The amounts represent a snapshot as of a moment in time. Market conditions, rates, expenses and other circumstances of operation continually fluctuate. As such, the recipient should consider the information herein to be out of date and expired as soon as it is received. PS Advantage, Inc. (“PSA”) reserves the right to change the information at any time. PSA, its affiliates, and their employees and agents make no representations, warranties or guaranties of any kind as to the actual results, including actual revenues, expenses or occupancy, to be achieved if PSA were to manage these facilities. The information herein is presented without any right of reliance by the recipient – you should do your own due diligence. This document is non-binding, is not a contract, is not an offer and does not create any legally binding obligations. No such obligations will exist unless and until you and PSA execute a definitive written agreement. The parties have no obligation to negotiate further. Any binding agreement with you is subject to approval by PSA’s relevant officers.

5 Year Summary|B53|DISCLAIMER: The amounts presented herein are based upon information provided by the intended recipient and numerous other assumptions. The amounts represent a snapshot as of a moment in time. Market conditions, rates, expenses and other circumstances of operation continually fluctuate. As such, the recipient should consider the information herein to be out of date and expired as soon as it is received. PS Advantage, Inc. (“PSA”) reserves the right to change the information at any time. PSA, its affiliates, and their employees and agents make no representations, warranties or guaranties of any kind as to the actual results, including actual revenues, expenses or occupancy, to be achieved if PSA were to manage these facilities. The information herein is presented without any right of reliance by the recipient – you should do your own due diligence. This document is non-binding, is not a contract, is not an offer and does not create any legally binding obligations. No such obligations will exist unless and until you and PSA execute a definitive written agreement. The parties have no obligation to negotiate further. Any binding agreement with you is subject to approval by PSA’s relevant officers.
